> On Mon, Mar 20, 2006 at 03:45:23PM +0100, Oliver Neukum wrote:
> >  static inline void *kcalloc(size_t n, size_t size, gfp_t flags)
> >  {
> > -	if (n != 0 && size > INT_MAX / n)
> > +	if (unlikely(size != 0 && n > INT_MAX / size ))
